Damn it...

284
00:18:30.751 --> 00:18:31.542
Hurry!

285
00:18:58.729 --> 00:18:59.690
That way!

286
00:19:09.790 --> 00:19:11.081
Come quick! Hurry!

287
00:19:35.646 --> 00:19:37.898
