Those people seem to have been affected by the attack.

296
00:19:57.958 --> 00:19:59.380
What the hell?

297
00:20:25.486 --> 00:20:26.527
What the fuck?

298
00:20:48.799 --> 00:20:49.930
What the hell is this?

299
00:21:20.080 --> 00:21:22.213
What are those freaks doing?

300
00:21:28.088 --> 00:21:29.970
Turn off the light

301
