What about those students?

302
00:22:13.924 --> 00:22:15.636
Do something. you're a policeman!

303
00:22:15.726 --> 00:22:17.178
We're not safe here. either.

304
00:22:17.228 --> 00:22:18.849
Let's just wait for backup.

305
00:22:18.849 --> 00:22:20.431
So we're going to stand here

306
00:22:20.481 --> 00:22:22.643
