307
00:22:24.024 --> 00:22:25.065
Hyun-seok...

308
00:22:29.029 --> 00:22:32.533
It looks like they're going towards that sign.

309
00:22:32.823 --> 00:22:34.325
Huh? The sign?

310
00:22:41.752 --> 00:22:43.204
We can lure them with these.

311
00:22:44.295 --> 00:22:45.166
Those?

312
00:22:45.666 --> 00:22:47.418
What will you do with them?

313
00:22:48.549 --> 00:22:50.301
Use this. my wheelchair!

314
00:22:50.341 --> 00:22:52.963
What are you talking about?

315
00:22:52.963 --> 00:22:55.176
What'll you do without it?

316
00:22:55.346 --> 00:22:56.557
Didn't you see earlier?

317
00:22:57.017 --> 00:23:00.100
If I'm going to get out. I won't be able to do it on this.

318
00:23:01.562 --> 00:23:04.064
We can't just let those people die.

319
00:23:13.984 --> 00:23:15.446
Fuck!

320
00:23:44.855 --> 00:23:45.766
Hurry!

321
00:23:47.358 --> 00:23:48.319
What?

322
00:23:48.319 --> 00:23:49.770
I can't. There's no way.

323
00:23:52.693 --> 00:23:54.235
Hey. don't go out there!

324
00:24:00.951 --> 00:24:01.912
This way!

325
00:24:03.083 --> 00:24:04.124
Hurry!

326
00:24:14.175 --> 00:24:15.386
Shut up. will you?

327
00:24:15.466 --> 00:24:16.257
Hurry!

328
00:24:30.981 --> 00:24:32.022
Why'd she do that?

329
00:24:33.234 --> 00:24:34.525
I'll go get her.

330
00:24:47.788 --> 00:24:49.210
Come. let's go.

331
00:24:49.580 --> 00:24:50.881
Come with me.

332
00:24:50.881 --> 00:24:53.584
You can do it. Let's go.

333
00:24:53.794 --> 00:24:55.836
Take my hand and go.

334
00:24:56.177 --> 00:24:58.088
Let's go. hurry.

335
00:25:03.144 --> 00:25:04.145
Kyu-seong!

336
00:25:15.606 --> 00:25:17.608
Come here. asshole!

337
00:25:20.571 --> 00:25:22.453
Get in. hurry!

338
00:26:19.920 --> 00:26:21.802
If I say our company's main business

339
00:26:21.842 --> 00:26:23.474
is collective intelligence...

340
00:26:23.554 --> 00:26:24.975
"Why is a bio company.

341
00:26:25.015 --> 00:26:28.179
rather than an IT company. studying that topic?"

342
00:26:28.679 --> 00:26:30.351
These fellows upgrade themselves

343
00:26:30.391 --> 00:26:31.982
through information exchange.

344
00:26:35.316 --> 00:26:38.239
Collective intelligence is a key force driving evolution.

345
00:27:18.859 --> 00:27:20.030
Kyu-seong!

346
00:27:20.691 --> 00:27:21.822
Hurry!

347
00:27:25.366 --> 00:27:26.447
No!

348
00:28:05.576 --> 00:28:08.239
This afternoon. the Doongwoori Building

349
00:28:08.239 --> 00:28:11.912
was locked down following an act of bio-terrorism.

350
00:28:12.163 --> 00:28:15.456
Health authorities designated the location a terrorism zone.

351
00:28:15.586 --> 00:28:18.289
and a full quarantine is in effect until an investigation...

352
00:28:18.289 --> 00:28:19.920
The Counterterrorism HQ says

353
00:28:19.960 --> 00:28:22.503
the virus in question is highly contagious

354
00:28:22.713 --> 00:28:24.635
and spreads extremely quickly.

355
00:28:24.715 --> 00:28:27.508
The Disease Control Agency is devoting all its resources

356
00:28:27.598 --> 00:28:28.599
to obtaining

357
00:28:28.599 --> 00:28:29.890
and researching possible vaccines.

358
00:28:29.930 --> 00:28:31.262
Meanwhile. unconfirmed rumors

359
00:28:31.352 --> 00:28:32.803
