361
00:28:35.476 --> 00:28:37.017
SWAT deployment complete.

362
00:28:37.017 --> 00:28:39.019
Double barricade of Doongwoori Building in place.

363
00:28:39.190 --> 00:28:40.401
Visual confirmation.

364
00:28:54.495 --> 00:28:56.327
Hello. shoppers.

365
00:28:56.667 --> 00:29:00.631
Thank you for visiting Doongwoori Shopping Mall today.

366
00:29:01.422 --> 00:29:04.545
The shopping mall is now closing.

367
00:29:05.296 --> 00:29:08.589
We look forward to welcoming you tomorrow

368
00:29:08.639 --> 00:29:10.721
