369
00:29:11.512 --> 00:29:15.596
We wish you a comfortable and safe trip home.

370
00:29:15.846 --> 00:29:16.647
Thank you.

371
00:29:16.647 --> 00:29:18.769
Shit. the data's not working.

372
00:29:19.230 --> 00:29:20.851
I'm okay. Yeah.

373
00:29:22.193 --> 00:29:23.484
And you. Dad?

374
00:29:24.525 --> 00:29:26.447
My Dearest Daughter

375
00:29:27.158 --> 00:29:28.739
Really? Thank God...

376
00:29:34.034 --> 00:29:35.246
Dad!

377
00:29:36.617 --> 00:29:38.999
- Who are you? Where's my dad? - Did Dad answer?

378
00:29:40.421 --> 00:29:41.962
Ji-hye. go to Grandma for a sec.

379
00:29:42.373 --> 00:29:43.964
- Why? - Just for a sec.

380
00:29:44.044 --> 00:29:45.216
Mom. take her.

381
00:29:45.216 --> 00:29:47.218
Right. come with me for a minute.

382
00:29:53.474 --> 00:29:54.635
What...

383
00:29:57.017 --> 00:29:58.729
What about Kyu-seong?

384
00:30:02.313 --> 00:30:03.984
Did he go somewhere?

385
00:30:06.447 --> 00:30:07.778
Kyu-seong...

386
00:30:09.320 --> 00:30:12.323
saved some people. and then...

387
00:30:13.204 --> 00:30:14.365
Who...

388
00:30:14.955 --> 00:30:16.457
Who did he save?

389
00:30:16.907 --> 00:30:18.789
Everything just sucks!

390
00:30:19.119 --> 00:30:20.371
And then what?

391
00:30:21.001 --> 00:30:23.624
And then what happened?

392
00:30:31.222 --> 00:30:32.973
-Kyu-seong... - Dad!

393
00:30:41.101 --> 00:30:42.433
What are you talking about?

394
00:30:43.023 --> 00:30:45.396
You know how long I've been stuck here?

395
00:30:47.438 --> 00:30:50.151
You won't get infected unless you're bitten!

396
00:30:51.192 --> 00:30:52.363
What did you say?

397
00:30:55.746 --> 00:30:56.787
What's this?

398
00:30:57.077 --> 00:30:58.409
What do you think?

399
00:31:01.121 --> 00:31:02.453
You're going to carry me?

400
00:31:02.623 --> 00:31:04.255
Who else is going to carry you?

401
00:31:05.005 --> 00:31:06.797
Think of it as going camping.

402
00:31:07.127 --> 00:31:11.672
This is why you should think twice before helping others.

403
00:31:14.635 --> 00:31:16.096
Listen. Officer!

404
00:31:16.217 --> 00:31:18.559
There's a rescue team coming to get us. right?

405
00:31:20.721 --> 00:31:21.722
The rescue team

406
00:31:23.474 --> 00:31:24.685
can't come in here.

407
00:31:24.815 --> 00:31:25.606
What?

408
00:31:26.106 --> 00:31:27.568
What are you saying?

409
00:31:27.568 --> 00:31:29.150
We're all still alive!

410
00:31:29.320 --> 00:31:31.652
The news has reported that this virus

411
00:31:31.692 --> 00:31:33.444
is unbelievably contagious.

412
00:31:33.444 --> 00:31:35.656
Until an epidemiological analysis is done.

413
00:31:35.696 --> 00:31:37.538
this building is under quarantine.

414
00:31:37.618 --> 00:31:38.909
Then what about us?

415
00:31:38.909 --> 00:31:41.242
They're telling us to just die here?

416
00:31:41.332 --> 00:31:42.743
I don't wanna die...

417
00:31:42.743 --> 00:31:44.835
- I don't wanna die! - I'm going fucking crazy...

418
00:31:44.915 --> 00:31:47.498
Fuck. you know how much I pay this country in taxes?

419
00:31:47.498 --> 00:31:49.800
But they won't save me?

420
00:31:50.801 --> 00:31:54.755
There is one way that we can be saved.

421
00:31:55.135 --> 00:31:56.467
What's that?

422
00:31:56.557 --> 00:31:59.390
The man behind this attack. Suh Young-chul.

423
00:31:59.430 --> 00:32:01.852
says he's injected the vaccine into his own body.

424
00:32:01.932 --> 00:32:04.895
If we find him and bring him out. we can all be rescued.

425
00:32:05.015 --> 00:32:06.397
Where is he?

426
00:32:07.188 --> 00:32:10.441
It's said he attended the seminar in this building today.

427
00:32:10.651 --> 00:32:12.823
and there's no sign that he left.

428
00:32:13.864 --> 00:32:15.326
Suh Young-chul...

429
00:32:15.866 --> 00:32:18.529
came to meet Chains Bio CEO Kang Woo-cheol.

430
00:32:19.200 --> 00:32:20.030
That's right.

431
00:32:20.161 --> 00:32:20.911
How'd you know that?

432
00:32:20.911 --> 00:32:22.163
After the seminar.

433
00:32:22.203 --> 00:32:25.496
I saw him by Kang's VIP Room on the 3rd floor.

434
00:32:25.536 --> 00:32:27.668
You must be a professor.

435
00:32:27.788 --> 00:32:29.460
Then where did he go?

436
00:32:29.500 --> 00:32:32.793
I saw him follow Kang into the room.

437
00:32:33.003 --> 00:32:34.635
So what are we supposed to do?

438
00:32:34.965 --> 00:32:36.717
We can't even set foot outside this door!

439
00:32:36.717 --> 00:32:40.301
Go up to the 3rd floor? How can we make it there?

440
00:32:40.391 --> 00:32:41.512
Right...

441
00:32:42.052 --> 00:32:43.474
Those people out there

442
00:32:44.054 --> 00:32:46.857
seem to be evolving through information exchange.

443
00:32:47.228 --> 00:32:49.109
First they walked on all fours.

444
00:32:49.310 --> 00:32:51.021
and charged at signs.

445
00:32:51.652 --> 00:32:53.023
Now they walk on two feet

446
00:32:53.734 --> 00:32:55.776
and their ability to identify humans

447
00:32:55.776 --> 00:32:57.318
is slowly taking shape.

448
00:32:58.028 --> 00:32:59.820
They're exchanging info?

449
00:32:59.950 --> 00:33:02.163
How. by calling each other?

450
00:33:02.533 --> 00:33:04.665
Words are not the only way to communicate.

451
00:33:05.075 --> 00:33:06.377
Like fungi or mushrooms.

452
00:33:06.497 --> 00:33:07.878
many creatures other than humans

453
00:33:07.958 --> 00:33:09.580
have their own communication networks.

454
00:33:09.580 --> 00:33:13.334
For example. ants communicate by pheromones.

455
00:33:13.924 --> 00:33:16.046
And to expedite the exchange of pheromones.

456
00:33:16.136 --> 00:33:18.339
they create a communication network of mucus.

457
00:33:18.469 --> 00:33:22.012
So you're saying the infected people there.

458
00:33:22.433 --> 00:33:24.435
they're in a state resembling ants?

459
00:33:24.555 --> 00:33:26.687
If they have collective intelligence based

460
00:33:26.687 --> 00:33:27.978
on information exchange.

461
00:33:28.269 --> 00:33:30.811
perhaps we can input false information.

462
00:33:32.563 --> 00:33:34.775
What. they've turned into ants?

463
00:33:34.905 --> 00:33:37.948
So how do we give them false info?

464
00:33:38.489 --> 00:33:39.860
Show them fake news?

465
00:33:39.990 --> 00:33:42.203
Ants. too. often show errant behavior

466
00:33:42.243 --> 00:33:44.285
when receiving false information.

467
00:33:44.325 --> 00:33:46.917
For example. ant mills.

468
00:33:47.708 --> 00:33:49.500
Sometimes while exchanging pheromones.

469
00:33:49.710 --> 00:33:51.332
Ant Mill an error occurs.

470
00:33:51.462 --> 00:33:54.755
At such times. they form a giant circle in one spot

471
00:33:54.755 --> 00:33:57.928
and keep turning in place. unable to stop.

472
00:33:58.839 --> 00:34:00.181
Until they die.

473
00:34:00.471 --> 00:34:03.684
So how are we going to give them false information?

474
00:34:04.054 --> 00:34:08.018
If one of us went to them giving off a special odor.

475
00:34:08.309 --> 00:34:10.100
and the rest of us stood still.

476
00:34:10.100 --> 00:34:12.443
giving off a completely different odor.

477
00:34:12.603 --> 00:34:15.146
I don't think they'd be able to recognize us as humans.

478
00:34:15.736 --> 00:34:18.199
Then until they figure out their mistake.

479
00:34:18.529 --> 00:34:20.451
we can buy ourselves some time.

480
00:34:21.742 --> 00:34:23.704
Who's gonna do that?

481
00:34:24.155 --> 00:34:25.246
I'll do it.

482
00:34:26.157 --> 00:34:27.828
You'll fail. 100%.

483
00:34:28.459 --> 00:34:31.662
Look. how about someone more fit?

484
00:34:32.293 --> 00:34:33.754
This guy should do.

485
00:34:33.914 --> 00:34:35.045
I'll do it.

486
00:34:35.045 --> 00:34:36.717
I said I'll do it.

487
00:34:37.758 --> 00:34:39.880
You're looking down on me because of my age.

488
00:34:40.221 --> 00:34:41.672
But in my 20s. I won a gold medal

489
00:34:41.672 --> 00:34:43.554
in a national track and field competition.

490
00:34:43.554 --> 00:34:44.925
Yeah sure. you stay out.

491
00:34:46.307 --> 00:34:47.308
That hurts! Ouch!

492
00:34:50.100 --> 00:34:52.183
I coached track and field before retiring.

493
00:34:52.483 --> 00:34:55.856
Professor. tell me what I should do.

494
00:35:04.865 --> 00:35:06.577
Where should I put this?

495
00:35:06.577 --> 00:35:07.748
Here.

496
00:35:07.948 --> 00:35:09.290
- Here? - Yeah.

497
00:35:09.290 --> 00:35:11.872
I added you all to a group chat. so check it.

498
00:35:12.543 --> 00:35:16.167
If they're exchanging information. we should do it. too.

499
00:35:33.023 --> 00:35:35.436
Bring back this same perfume.

500
00:35:45.536 --> 00:35:48.038
Hey. you nutjobs!

501
00:35:48.619 --> 00:35:49.910
Come and get me!

502
00:37:13.994 --> 00:37:15.125
Hurry!

503
00:37:15.496 --> 00:37:17.127
Close the door!

504
00:37:18.789 --> 00:37:20.421
I got them. Here.

505
00:37:32.933 --> 00:37:33.053
That antifreeze. bring it here

506
00:37:33.053 --> 00:37:34.305
That antifreeze. bring it here!

507
00:37:34.305 --> 00:37:35.436
Antifreeze. okay!

508
00:37:40.151 --> 00:37:40.941
Here.

509
00:37:40.981 --> 00:37:42.062
That stinks!

510
00:37:42.193 --> 00:37:44.024
Why does this smell so strong?

511
00:38:04.425 --> 00:38:05.756
Ready? - Yeah.

512
00:40:15.886 --> 00:40:17.348
We can go now.

513
00:40:37.198 --> 00:40:37.988
Hurry up!

514
00:40:40.080 --> 00:40:41.282
Let's just go!

515
00:40:45.035 --> 00:40:46.167
What are you doing?

516
00:40:48.789 --> 00:40:50.631
Does anyone have a lighter?

517
00:41:20.741 --> 00:41:21.662
Hurry. run!

518
00:41:23.204 --> 00:41:24.325
Behind us!

519
00:41:45.766 --> 00:41:46.807
Run. quickly!

520
00:41:51.902 --> 00:41:52.943
Hold on tight.

521
00:42:13.294 --> 00:42:14.215
Look out!

522
00:42:52.833 --> 00:42:55.085
How did a world-renowned scientist

523
00:42:55.085 --> 00:42:57.798
become a terrorist threateniing the nation?

524
00:42:58.008 --> 00:43:01.011
Let's look into the background of Dr. Suh Young-chul.

525
00:43:01.131 --> 00:43:02.923
He was top-ranked at his university

526
00:43:02.973 --> 00:43:04.515
from entrance to graduation.

527
00:43:04.725 --> 00:43:08.018
and his graduation thesis "Biocomputing With Fungi"

528
00:43:08.179 --> 00:43:10.771
was published in the journal Science.

529
00:43:10.981 --> 00:43:13.396
For such a promising talent

530
00:43:13.396 --> 00:43:14.597
to suddenly commit terrorism

531
00:43:14.597 --> 00:43:15.798
and hold the nation hostage.

532
00:43:15.798 --> 00:43:17.843
it's quite hard to understand.

533
00:43:18.043 --> 00:43:18.887
Reporter Kim Seong-il.

534
00:43:18.887 --> 00:43:20.872
are there any notable details

535
00:43:20.872 --> 00:43:22.597
concerning Suh Young-chul ?

536
00:43:22.797 --> 00:43:26.297
Suh's father was a professor of Applied Biology

537
00:43:26.297 --> 00:43:28.569
at Seocheong University.

538
00:43:28.569 --> 00:43:29.702
PROF. SUH DENIES MISUSE OF RESEARCH FUNDS
While he was there.

539
00:43:29.702 --> 00:43:32.507
PROF. SUH DENIES MISUSE OF RESEARCH FUNDS
an anonymous tip led to an internal report

540
00:43:32.507 --> 00:43:34.874
on misuse of funds for his research lab

541
00:43:34.874 --> 00:43:36.918
and exploitation of student researchers.

542
00:43:36.918 --> 00:43:38.872
and this was widely covered in the press.

543
00:43:38.872 --> 00:43:41.042
Four weeks after the report

544
00:43:41.042 --> 00:43:43.720
Professor Suh chose to end his own life.

545
00:43:43.720 --> 00:43:45.996
Is there any link between this incident

546
00:43:45.996 --> 00:43:48.403
and Suh Young-chul's terrorist attack ?

547
00:43:48.603 --> 00:43:51.562
Could it be some sort of revenge?

548
00:43:51.892 --> 00:43:55.316
So far. Suh has not made any requests or demands.

549
00:43:55.356 --> 00:43:58.819
so it seems unlikely that the two incidents are related.

550
00:43:58.899 --> 00:44:01.442
At the moment. the government has not released

551
00:44:01.442 --> 00:44:03.324
any information about the attack.

552
00:44:05.406 --> 00:44:06.487
3rd Floor.

553
00:44:16.747 --> 00:44:17.748
No one here.

554
00:44:17.798 --> 00:44:18.629
Hurry!

555
00:44:47.908 --> 00:44:49.530
Suh Young-chul. you are under arrest

556
00:44:49.580 --> 00:44:51.742
for the Doongwoori Building terrorist attack.

557
00:44:51.992 --> 00:44:54.585
You have the right to an attorney.

558
00:44:54.585 --> 00:44:56.417
and the right to remain silent.

559
00:44:56.667 --> 00:44:59.630
Anything you say can and will be used against you in court...

560
00:44:59.630 --> 00:45:00.751
Nice to meet you.

561
00:45:01.172 --> 00:45:04.134
Using water to disrupt their communications network.

562
00:45:04.755 --> 00:45:06.637
that was your idea. Professor Kwon?

563
00:45:07.047 --> 00:45:07.798
What's this?

564
00:45:07.798 --> 00:45:09.220
You two know each other?

565
00:45:09.320 --> 00:45:10.511
But that was a mistake.

566
00:45:12.973 --> 00:45:15.015
Water evaporates quickly.

567
00:45:15.146 --> 00:45:17.898
If water mixes in the air with their network.

568
00:45:17.938 --> 00:45:19.270
won't it work faster?

569
00:45:19.940 --> 00:45:20.811
Forget it.

570
00:45:21.562 --> 00:45:22.653
What now?

571
00:45:23.154 --> 00:45:24.405
Is the rescue team coming?

572
00:45:25.065 --> 00:45:25.906
No.

573
00:45:26.277 --> 00:45:28.529
We have to meet the rescue team on the roof.

574
00:45:28.529 --> 00:45:29.029
What?

575
00:45:29.029 --> 00:45:31.162
The rescue team must not be exposed to the infected.

576
00:45:31.162 --> 00:45:34.955
We almost died coming here. now we have to go to the roof?

577
00:45:35.125 --> 00:45:38.078
Can't the rescue team come down and wipe them all out?

578
00:45:38.789 --> 00:45:40.291
Those people are patients.

579
00:45:40.631 --> 00:45:42.833
We've been ordered not to kill them without reason.

580
00:45:42.883 --> 00:45:44.465
What bullshit!

581
00:45:44.505 --> 00:45:46.177
Those monsters out there are patients?

582
00:45:46.677 --> 00:45:48.299
Do patients kill people?

583
00:45:49.430 --> 00:45:52.303
Damn it. I don't care if they're monsters or whatever.

584
00:45:52.513 --> 00:45:55.556
At any rate. if we can get him up to the roof.

585
00:45:55.686 --> 00:45:58.689
the rescue team will come. Then we can all survive.

586
00:45:58.899 --> 00:46:01.522
We just need to find a safe way to get there.

587
00:46:02.273 --> 00:46:03.944
Is there one?

588
00:46:04.104 --> 00:46:05.105
There is.

589
00:46:05.236 --> 00:46:08.989
There's a cargo elevator that most people don't know about.

590
00:46:10.531 --> 00:46:12.613
That seems safest.

591
00:46:13.284 --> 00:46:15.366
I think that security guard's right.

592
00:46:18.369 --> 00:46:21.081
Alright. let's give it a try.

593
00:46:21.462 --> 00:46:23.214
You take the lead.

594
00:46:27.218 --> 00:46:28.509
Let's go.

595
00:46:30.471 --> 00:46:31.512
You first.

596
00:46:36.307 --> 00:46:37.388
Professor Gong!

597
00:46:41.602 --> 00:46:44.235
You got here quickly.

598
00:46:44.395 --> 00:46:45.236
Yes.

599
00:46:46.607 --> 00:46:48.489
This was Suh Young-chul's research lab?

600
00:46:48.489 --> 00:46:49.150
Yeah.

601
00:46:49.320 --> 00:46:54.245
After leaving Chains Bio. it seems he kept researching here.

602
00:46:54.615 --> 00:46:55.576
Professor Joo!

603
00:46:55.656 --> 00:46:56.537
Yeah.

604
00:46:57.208 --> 00:47:00.251
Say hello. This is Myunghan University Biotechnology

605
00:47:00.291 --> 00:47:01.712
Professor Gong Sul-hee.

606
00:47:02.543 --> 00:47:05.125
These are professors Lee Hyeon-myeong and Jo Hyeon-mi.

607
00:47:05.125 --> 00:47:07.087
So the government has assembled

608
00:47:07.127 --> 00:47:09.170
this special investigative team.

609
00:47:09.170 --> 00:47:11.922
When the SWAT team goes in. we'll join them.

610
00:47:12.173 --> 00:47:13.804
so prepare yourself. Professor Gong.

611
00:47:13.804 --> 00:47:15.055
Understood.

612
00:47:15.806 --> 00:47:17.428
Alpha Team take the front door.

613
00:47:17.478 --> 00:47:19.180
Delta Team enter from the back.

614
00:47:36.617 --> 00:47:37.658
Shit...

615
00:47:38.329 --> 00:47:39.700
I'm gonna do it.

616
00:47:39.950 --> 00:47:41.162
I'm pushing it.

617
00:47:51.922 --> 00:47:53.264
Hurry up!

618
00:47:54.175 --> 00:47:55.386
Hurry!

619
00:47:56.387 --> 00:47:57.848
Close the door. quick!

620
00:48:03.394 --> 00:48:04.775
Going up.

621
00:48:07.067 --> 00:48:09.480
We'll be on the roof in 5 minutes.

622
00:48:12.783 --> 00:48:14.325
How old are you?

623
00:48:15.236 --> 00:48:17.158
You're in great shape for your age.

624
00:48:18.289 --> 00:48:20.241
The way you slid back there was so cool.

625
00:48:21.162 --> 00:48:22.623
You were so fast.

626
00:48:23.334 --> 00:48:24.205
Like this.

627
00:48:27.548 --> 00:48:28.459
The doors are opening.

628
00:48:46.267 --> 00:48:47.067
No!

629
00:49:11.462 --> 00:49:12.843
He got away!

630
00:49:14.295 --> 00:49:15.846
Who cares if he did?

631
00:49:16.347 --> 00:49:19.470
You really think that bastard's more important than us?

632
00:49:19.470 --> 00:49:21.182
That jerk is the vaccine.

633
00:49:21.392 --> 00:49:24.605
You saw it now. The infected didn't even touch him.

634
00:49:24.805 --> 00:49:26.687
We need to take that vaccine out with us!

635
00:49:26.807 --> 00:49:27.978
But...

636
00:49:28.559 --> 00:49:30.561
How are we supposed to bring him out?

637
00:49:30.561 --> 00:49:34.155
You saw how those monsters are swarming all over!

638
00:49:34.695 --> 00:49:37.158
How do we pull him out of there?

639
00:49:38.118 --> 00:49:39.200
The doors are opening.

640
00:49:48.959 --> 00:49:52.503
What? Are those bastards mimicking us?

641
00:49:57.968 --> 00:49:59.590
The doors are closing.

642
00:50:04.054 --> 00:50:05.596
What do we do now?

643
00:50:06.347 --> 00:50:07.598
-Hyun-seok. - Yeah?

644
00:50:07.648 --> 00:50:09.150
Is there a control room where

645
00:50:09.190 --> 00:50:11.101
you can see all the building's CCTVs?

646
00:50:11.101 --> 00:50:12.403
What? A control room?

647
00:50:12.733 --> 00:50:14.735
You should know. you're on the security team.

648
00:50:14.735 --> 00:50:15.316
Yeah.

649
00:50:15.316 --> 00:50:18.359
If we can watch all of the CCTVs.

650
00:50:18.449 --> 00:50:21.452
we can see where he's going in real time.

651
00:50:21.952 --> 00:50:23.454
The control room...

652
00:50:24.535 --> 00:50:26.417
is at the very end of Floor B2.

653
00:50:26.417 --> 00:50:27.998
B2! B2!

654
00:50:28.038 --> 00:50:30.871
For now. let's go there and look for Suh.

655
00:50:42.843 --> 00:50:44.134
Alpha. clear.

656
00:50:45.055 --> 00:50:46.387
Delta. clear.

657
00:50:47.188 --> 00:50:49.560
He's set up an entire lab here.

658
00:51:03.244 --> 00:51:05.075
You should see this over here.

659
00:51:21.262 --> 00:51:24.175
What is this? Are they all dead?

660
00:51:24.925 --> 00:51:26.227
They're alive.

661
00:51:33.063 --> 00:51:35.186
What experiment was he doing?

662
00:51:43.284 --> 00:51:45.536
Here! This one's been opened!

663
00:51:48.409 --> 00:51:49.540
Contact!

664
00:52:32.543 --> 00:52:33.834
SPECIAL OPERATION UNIT

665
00:52:40.671 --> 00:52:41.712
Attack!

666
00:52:42.383 --> 00:52:43.554
Return fire!

667
00:52:44.805 --> 00:52:45.716
Alpha down!

668
00:52:54.014 --> 00:52:55.316
Contact!

669
00:52:56.437 --> 00:52:58.399
Take her to safety!

670
00:53:36.897 --> 00:53:39.610
Targets have stopped moving. Clear. confirming.

671
00:53:39.980 --> 00:53:41.402
Clear. confirming.

672
00:53:46.066 --> 00:53:47.408
They've all stopped.

673
00:53:48.159 --> 00:53:49.620
Each defend your own zone.

674
00:53:49.660 --> 00:53:51.952
In case of danger. respond immediately.

675
00:54:39.290 --> 00:54:39.670
What's that?

676
00:54:40.541 --> 00:54:42.082
That's evolving?

677
00:54:43.334 --> 00:54:45.045
Where's the control room?

678
00:54:45.586 --> 00:54:46.627
That way.

679
00:54:46.677 --> 00:54:48.469
Okay. let's move quietly.

680
00:55:55.075 --> 00:55:56.577
Pull yourself together!

681
00:56:17.388 --> 00:56:18.599
Sit me down here.

682
00:56:18.889 --> 00:56:20.181
Close that.

683
00:56:26.397 --> 00:56:28.649
These are the main cameras.

684
00:56:29.280 --> 00:56:30.691
And for the auxiliary cams...

685
00:56:30.731 --> 00:56:31.652
CCTV.

686
00:56:33.784 --> 00:56:35.786
What floor did Suh get off on?

687
00:56:36.157 --> 00:56:37.117
8th floor?

688
00:56:37.448 --> 00:56:39.580
The 9th floor. I'll start looking there.

689
00:56:46.587 --> 00:56:48.709
You're in great shape for your age.

690
00:56:49.300 --> 00:56:51.342
The way you slid back there was so cool.

691
00:56:51.552 --> 00:56:53.003
You were so fast.

692
00:56:53.424 --> 00:56:55.386
How could Suh have known?

693
00:56:56.847 --> 00:56:58.309
The things he said in the elevator.

694
00:56:58.429 --> 00:57:00.431
as if he'd watched what we'd done.

695
00:57:02.603 --> 00:57:03.604
You're right.

696
00:57:04.515 --> 00:57:06.727
Is he watching CCTVs like us?

697
00:57:08.729 --> 00:57:12.653
If Suh can see through the eyes of the infected...

698
00:57:14.155 --> 00:57:15.196
Hold on. then...

699
00:57:16.157 --> 00:57:18.028
Whatever these monsters see.

700
00:57:18.739 --> 00:57:20.491
Suh can see the same thing?

701
00:57:20.701 --> 00:57:22.583
He sees the same thing? What the hell?

702
00:57:22.703 --> 00:57:23.704
I found him!

703
00:57:29.540 --> 00:57:31.422
Where's that bastard going?

704
00:57:55.946 --> 00:57:57.158
What's he doing?

705
00:58:01.662 --> 00:58:03.123
Where is he going?

706
00:58:05.206 --> 00:58:06.877
It seems he's searching for something.

707
00:58:07.378 --> 00:58:08.629
He stopped.

708
00:58:09.210 --> 00:58:10.581
Where is that?

709
00:58:10.921 --> 00:58:15.176
3rd Floor. Building A Hallway...

710
00:58:16.547 --> 00:58:17.678
Bro!

711
00:58:19.680 --> 00:58:22.473
You locked me up. so I had a hard time finding you.

712
00:58:28.439 --> 00:58:29.730
Oh. that's...

713
00:58:29.850 --> 00:58:31.692
CEO Kang Woo-cheol.

714
00:58:31.692 --> 00:58:32.653
Huh?

715
00:58:32.733 --> 00:58:34.815
The first person Suh met.

716
00:58:36.487 --> 00:58:39.570
He was probably the first infected.

717
00:58:46.707 --> 00:58:49.039
See. wasn't I right?

718
00:58:51.622 --> 00:58:54.835
I said you'd be my link to the new humanity.

719
00:58:55.256 --> 00:58:56.757
So hurry up and bite me.

720
00:59:08.138 --> 00:59:09.980
Wait. did he just bite him?

721
00:59:10.691 --> 00:59:11.482
What's happening to him?

722
00:59:26.157 --> 00:59:27.117
Look at them.

723
00:59:45.426 --> 00:59:47.097
I'm not sure what it is.

724
00:59:47.808 --> 00:59:49.390
but they must be receiving some

725
00:59:49.430 --> 00:59:51.272
completely new sort of information.

726
00:59:53.274 --> 00:59:57.188
What is it? Is it connected to Suh being bitten?

727
00:59:57.278 --> 00:59:59.029
I have no idea.

728
00:59:59.820 --> 01:00:02.903
Then how long will they be in this condition?

729
01:00:03.324 --> 01:00:05.156
Before. they were like that for several minutes.

730
01:00:05.156 --> 01:00:06.947
There's no way to know.

731
01:00:08.579 --> 01:00:10.291
Okay. this is our chance.

732
01:00:10.411 --> 01:00:13.204
While they're in that state. we should go get the vaccine.

733
01:00:13.624 --> 01:00:15.876
He's on the 3rd floor. it won't take long.

734
01:00:17.758 --> 01:00:20.421
I'll watch the CCTV from here

735
01:00:20.551 --> 01:00:23.053
and tell you where it's safe. through the group chat.

736
01:00:23.264 --> 01:00:25.716
What you?

737
01:00:27.888 --> 01:00:28.929
You're going to stay here?

738
01:00:28.929 --> 01:00:30.561
Get the vaccine and come back.

739
01:00:30.601 --> 01:00:32.813
Until then. I'll tell you where to go.

740
01:00:33.103 --> 01:00:35.065
How can I leave you behind?

741
01:00:35.646 --> 01:00:38.729
Listen to me. This is the safest way.

742
01:00:39.780 --> 01:00:40.941
Yes. let's do that.

743
01:00:41.031 --> 01:00:43.944
We don't know when they'll wake up. so let's hurry.

744
01:01:34.995 --> 01:01:37.498
Let's drag him to someplace safe.

745
01:01:43.464 --> 01:01:46.467
What's going on?

746
01:01:53.474 --> 01:01:54.395
Go. quick!

747
01:01:55.226 --> 01:01:56.767
Hurry! Run!

748
01:02:03.234 --> 01:02:04.695
Hurry! Get inside!

749
01:02:04.985 --> 01:02:06.026
Hurry!

750
01:02:10.070 --> 01:02:12.032
What is this freak doing?

751
01:02:14.745 --> 01:02:16.627
They're leaving.

752
01:02:47.408 --> 01:02:48.699
Go that way.

753
01:02:54.865 --> 01:02:56.116
This way. quickly!

754
01:03:17.888 --> 01:03:19.139
They're gone.

755
01:03:20.100 --> 01:03:21.772
What the hell did you do?

756
01:03:25.316 --> 01:03:28.989
Ah. did you only pretend to go out? You're smart.

757
01:03:29.900 --> 01:03:31.782
You think if you cover my eyes.

758
01:03:31.782 --> 01:03:34.245
you'll be able to get out of here alive?

759
01:03:34.325 --> 01:03:35.746
What's this freak yammering about?

760
01:03:36.657 --> 01:03:38.619
Since getting bitten by Kang Woo-cheol.

761
01:03:38.659 --> 01:03:40.751
it seems he can communicate with all of them.

762
01:03:41.162 --> 01:03:42.333
Wait. then...

763
01:03:42.793 --> 01:03:46.797
that means he can control all those monsters out there.

764
01:03:48.128 --> 01:03:50.301
Let's only communicate by texting.

765
01:03:50.341 --> 01:03:52.513
Don't let him see or hear anything.

766
01:04:06.607 --> 01:04:09.610
But didn't we file all of our reports already?

767
01:04:10.070 --> 01:04:12.283
Why are they calling us to the Counterterrorism HQ?

768
01:04:12.323 --> 01:04:14.575
We'll see when we get there.

769
01:04:39.139 --> 01:04:41.182
From office go straight to emergency exit.

770
01:04:42.102 --> 01:04:43.144
Up stairs to 4th floor. to machine room.

771
01:04:47.278 --> 01:04:48.439
Let's hurry.

772
01:05:11.632 --> 01:05:12.713
Wait a minute.

773
01:05:14.925 --> 01:05:17.968
We're going back to where we started.

774
01:05:19.059 --> 01:05:20.261
That's right. Why?

775
01:05:21.312 --> 01:05:22.763
We need to pick up my sister.

776
01:05:22.813 --> 01:05:25.976
But now we can get out with the vaccine.

777
01:05:26.317 --> 01:05:27.478
Oh. that's right.

778
01:05:27.728 --> 01:05:30.110
This way. there's an elevator to the roof.

779
01:05:30.271 --> 01:05:31.942
What's going on?

780
01:05:32.022 --> 01:05:32.983
SECURITY

781
01:05:32.983 --> 01:05:34.985
What are you suggesting here?

782
01:05:35.025 --> 01:05:37.158
But now we just need to go up.

783
01:05:37.198 --> 01:05:38.989
You expect us to go back to the control room?

784
01:06:14.365 --> 01:06:17.027
Control Room

785
01:06:32.633 --> 01:06:33.714
What the hell?

786
01:06:33.754 --> 01:06:34.545
Hey!

787
01:06:34.755 --> 01:06:36.717
What do you think you're doing?

788
01:06:37.218 --> 01:06:38.219
-You... What?

789
01:06:38.259 --> 01:06:39.220
What did you do?

790
01:06:39.260 --> 01:06:40.301
Stop it.

791
01:06:40.471 --> 01:06:42.183
Make it fucking stop!

792
01:06:44.185 --> 01:06:45.596
I can't let this bastard go.

793
01:06:45.646 --> 01:06:48.599
I'm taking him with me. You. follow me!

794
01:06:49.480 --> 01:06:50.481
Come on!

795
01:06:50.731 --> 01:06:52.193
What are you doing?

796
01:06:52.313 --> 01:06:53.604
Are you crazy?

797
01:06:54.275 --> 01:06:55.946
Don't touch that vaccine!

798
01:06:59.280 --> 01:07:02.493
I'm sorry. but give up on your sister.

799
01:07:03.324 --> 01:07:04.205
It's too late.

800
01:07:35.065 --> 01:07:37.238
Hyun-seok

801
01:07:40.781 --> 01:07:42.533
Until he brings back his sister.

802
01:07:42.613 --> 01:07:43.994
we're going to wait here.

803
01:07:44.034 --> 01:07:45.246
Got it?

804
01:07:59.340 --> 01:08:00.761
Everyone listen up.

805
01:08:00.921 --> 01:08:04.305
This vaccine here is more important than anyone.

806
01:08:04.725 --> 01:08:06.767
This is for the whole world. okay?

807
01:08:11.932 --> 01:08:15.276
If you want to live. lead the way.

808
01:08:16.397 --> 01:08:17.568
Now!

809
01:08:32.122 --> 01:08:33.374
Hyun-seok!

810
01:08:33.624 --> 01:08:36.046
Are you okay? I'm going to you now.

811
01:08:36.046 --> 01:08:38.799
Which way is safe to go?

812
01:08:40.961 --> 01:08:42.713
Which way should I go?

813
01:08:43.714 --> 01:08:45.055
Hyun-hee!

814
01:08:47.388 --> 01:08:47.768
Um...

815
01:08:48.309 --> 01:08:50.471
Keep going straight ahead.

816
01:08:50.521 --> 01:08:51.972
and turn right.

817
01:08:55.025 --> 01:08:56.106
Okay. then what?

818
01:08:57.778 --> 01:08:59.570
This time. go left.

819
01:09:04.655 --> 01:09:06.577
Go straight. then take the stairs on the right.

820
01:09:06.737 --> 01:09:08.539
No no. stairs on the left!

821
01:09:08.659 --> 01:09:09.580
The left?

822
01:09:09.660 --> 01:09:10.581
Here? Is this right?

823
01:09:10.581 --> 01:09:11.292
Yeah.

824
01:09:11.292 --> 01:09:12.833
Go up those.

825
01:09:14.875 --> 01:09:16.207
Okay. I'm here.

826
01:09:16.457 --> 01:09:18.589
Go out the door and take the elevator.

827
01:09:18.629 --> 01:09:20.421
Here it is!

828
01:09:21.001 --> 01:09:22.092
I'm here!

829
01:09:22.092 --> 01:09:23.344
Are you okay?

830
01:09:27.308 --> 01:09:28.969
Hyun-hee. you made a mistake.

831
01:09:29.009 --> 01:09:31.562
this elevator doesn't go to the basement.

832
01:09:31.892 --> 01:09:33.854
You're all set now. Press the 4th floor.

833
01:09:34.475 --> 01:09:36.647
The 4th floor? Get off there?

834
01:09:36.647 --> 01:09:37.768
Hyun-seok...

835
01:09:38.229 --> 01:09:39.150
Then what?

836
01:09:39.190 --> 01:09:41.021
Listen closely to what I say.

837
01:09:41.192 --> 01:09:42.403
From the 4th floor.

838
01:09:42.443 --> 01:09:45.366
go right until you see an emergency stairway.

839
01:09:45.616 --> 01:09:47.988
Climb up to the 7th floor.

840
01:09:49.370 --> 01:09:53.494
Then you can rejoin the group you left.

841
01:09:55.496 --> 01:09:57.628
What are you talking about?

842
01:09:58.499 --> 01:09:59.710
Hyun-hee!

843
01:10:02.383 --> 01:10:03.254
Tell me quickly.

844
01:10:03.254 --> 01:10:04.425
Hyun-seok. focus!

845
01:10:04.425 --> 01:10:05.426
Hyun-hee!

846
01:10:05.426 --> 01:10:06.507
Hyun-seok!

847
01:10:08.138 --> 01:10:09.800
Get out of here alive.

848
01:10:09.930 --> 01:10:11.262
It's too late for me.

849
01:10:11.302 --> 01:10:13.684
No. it's not too late.

850
01:10:14.475 --> 01:10:17.728
It's not fucking late. I'll go there!

851
01:10:19.059 --> 01:10:21.272
I can go there now.

852
01:10:21.692 --> 01:10:23.023
Just tell me.

853
01:10:23.023 --> 01:10:25.065
We should've gone camping last week.

854
01:10:27.988 --> 01:10:30.161
Go on. I'll hang up now.

855
01:10:30.451 --> 01:10:32.873
Wait. don't ...

856
01:10:59.400 --> 01:11:00.771
Wait...

857
01:11:19.370 --> 01:11:21.212
What the hell?

858
01:11:23.123 --> 01:11:24.585
Oh no!

859
01:11:27.718 --> 01:11:29.470
You all killed my sister. I feel so bad!

860
01:11:29.970 --> 01:11:32.723
I'm going to kill that vaccine.

861
01:11:35.596 --> 01:11:38.769
And you you people will never get out of here alive.

862
01:11:50.491 --> 01:11:50.861
Is there even a plan?

863
01:11:50.861 --> 01:11:52.203
My brother is trapped in there.

864
01:11:53.364 --> 01:11:55.206
infected by some chemical weapon.

865
01:11:55.456 --> 01:11:57.158
They can't just leave him there!

866
01:11:57.248 --> 01:12:00.000
Please send in medical staff or someone right now!

867
01:12:00.161 --> 01:12:04.215
They keep telling us to wait. but how long can we wait here?

868
01:12:04.215 --> 01:12:05.336
Excuse me. Minister.

869
01:12:05.506 --> 01:12:06.667
They're here.

870
01:12:06.797 --> 01:12:07.838
Dear me.

871
01:12:10.341 --> 01:12:12.012
Thank you for coming.

872
01:12:12.132 --> 01:12:13.304
Just a second.

873
01:12:14.134 --> 01:12:16.597
I think we'll have to talk over there.

874
01:12:16.927 --> 01:12:18.519
Join us. Police Commissioner.

875
01:12:18.599 --> 01:12:19.560
Yes.

876
01:12:24.185 --> 01:12:26.647
I'll get right to the point.

877
01:12:26.987 --> 01:12:28.189
Let's say the people inside

878
01:12:28.239 --> 01:12:30.110
are in a state resembling those monkeys.

879
01:12:30.241 --> 01:12:33.284
Then what are the chances they can return to normal?

880
01:12:35.366 --> 01:12:37.538
Well...

881
01:12:37.748 --> 01:12:39.660
right now. we can't say with certainty..

882
01:12:39.830 --> 01:12:41.162
Very unlikely.

883
01:12:43.083 --> 01:12:45.796
What do you mean? Explain it simply.

884
01:12:46.417 --> 01:12:50.421
Nerve cells. once they're destroyed.

885
01:12:51.422 --> 01:12:53.514
cannot be healed or recovered.

886
01:12:55.466 --> 01:12:56.557
Put simply.

887
01:12:57.468 --> 01:13:01.392
once infected. they are more or less brain dead.

888
01:13:03.894 --> 01:13:07.148
Our squad leader has Suh Young-chul. right?

889
01:13:07.318 --> 01:13:08.229
Yes. he does.

890
01:13:08.279 --> 01:13:09.820
And the rescue team's on standby.

891
01:13:09.860 --> 01:13:11.572
since they can't hurt the infected.

892
01:13:11.652 --> 01:13:12.823
That's right.

893
01:13:13.574 --> 01:13:15.075
In that case.

894
01:13:15.236 --> 01:13:18.289
as the special investigative team explained to me just now.

895
01:13:18.409 --> 01:13:21.041
I'd like you to make a formal announcement.

896
01:13:21.162 --> 01:13:21.792
In particular...

897
01:13:22.703 --> 01:13:23.294
In particular...

898
01:13:24.915 --> 01:13:28.048
if Professor Gong Sul-hee. a victim's family member herself.

899
01:13:28.048 --> 01:13:30.591
makes an announcement about the state of the infected.

900
01:13:30.591 --> 01:13:33.003
citizens may be more willing to trust her.

901
01:13:34.215 --> 01:13:38.098
You're saying you want justification

902
01:13:38.098 --> 01:13:42.102
to shoot the infected people inside?

903
01:13:42.313 --> 01:13:43.564
With us taking responsibility?

904
01:13:43.604 --> 01:13:47.188
No. no responsibility. You say it's impossible to treat?

905
01:13:47.688 --> 01:13:49.440
So what's most important is to

906
01:13:49.480 --> 01:13:51.982
secure the vaccine to stop further spread.

907
01:13:51.982 --> 01:13:53.023
Right?

908
01:13:53.023 --> 01:13:56.487
Everything we've said up until now is speculation.

909
01:13:56.527 --> 01:13:58.078
Even if they're brain dead.

910
01:13:58.118 --> 01:14:00.451
we need more time to study it. Minister.

911
01:14:00.451 --> 01:14:01.282
Hold on.

912
01:14:01.372 --> 01:14:02.783
Why are you changing your position?

913
01:14:02.783 --> 01:14:03.954
We're not changing our position.

914
01:14:03.954 --> 01:14:06.917
- We're just stating facts! - Don't get upset.

915
01:14:06.917 --> 01:14:09.210
- You said there's no way to treat it. - What we mean is...

916
01:14:09.210 --> 01:14:10.881
I'll do it.

917
01:14:12.793 --> 01:14:15.426
Professor Gong. just a minute. This isn't right. hold on.

918
01:14:15.796 --> 01:14:17.178
And then...

919
01:14:17.758 --> 01:14:19.850
there's something else you have to do.

920
01:14:20.471 --> 01:14:22.973
Among the monkeys in Suh's lab.

921
01:14:23.354 --> 01:14:25.766
once the one marked #1 was killed.

922
01:14:25.806 --> 01:14:28.399
all the other monkeys stopped moving.

923
01:14:29.730 --> 01:14:31.402
What's that monkey #1?

924
01:14:31.402 --> 01:14:32.773
Based on his records.-

925
01:14:32.863 --> 01:14:35.526
this was the first monkey to be infected.

926
01:14:35.736 --> 01:14:37.488
So if we take out the first person

927
01:14:37.488 --> 01:14:39.200
in that building to be infected.

928
01:14:39.450 --> 01:14:42.573
all the others will stop moving. is that right?

929
01:14:43.033 --> 01:14:45.035
Yes. I believe so.

930
01:14:46.076 --> 01:14:48.249
Hold on. in that case...

931
01:14:50.040 --> 01:14:51.542
Let's do this.

932
01:14:52.082 --> 01:14:54.545
Call the security firm in charge of the building

933
01:14:54.585 --> 01:14:56.046
and get a link to the CCTV.

934
01:14:56.136 --> 01:14:58.429
Let's find out who was the first to get infected.

935
01:14:58.759 --> 01:15:02.803
Then under the name of Professor Gong.

936
01:15:02.893 --> 01:15:05.226
we'll issue a press release on the team's findings.

937
01:15:05.306 --> 01:15:06.557
Quickly. okay?

938
01:15:06.647 --> 01:15:08.979
Let's get this moving. Hurry up.

939
01:15:09.150 --> 01:15:10.271
Let's go.

940
01:15:17.608 --> 01:15:18.989
Have you gone mad?

941
01:15:19.160 --> 01:15:22.163
Don't you know if things go badly. they'll blame it on you?

942
01:15:23.113 --> 01:15:27.458
What's important now is not who's responsible.

943
01:15:28.709 --> 01:15:30.211
It's stopping more infections.

944
01:16:51.542 --> 01:16:53.834
We're sending you the link to the

945
01:16:53.834 --> 01:16:56.547
Doongwoori Building control room CCTV.

946
01:16:56.837 --> 01:16:57.958
Take a look.

947
01:16:58.169 --> 01:17:02.052
It was about noon yesterday when the incident occurred.

948
01:17:02.173 --> 01:17:05.176
Thoroughly investigate what happened in that building.

949
01:17:05.426 --> 01:17:06.847
What we need to find

950
01:17:06.847 --> 01:17:10.351
is the very first person infected in Suh's terrorist attack.

951
01:17:10.681 --> 01:17:11.101
-Got it? Yes. sir.

952
01:17:11.101 --> 01:17:12.393
Let's begin.

953
01:17:47.218 --> 01:17:48.559
...go up stairs to 31st floor lounge.

954
01:17:48.559 --> 01:17:50.681
then take emergency stairway to roof.

955
01:18:14.495 --> 01:18:15.286
There it is.

956
01:18:17.958 --> 01:18:20.751
This is an announcement of escape routes

957
01:18:20.751 --> 01:18:22.883
in case of fire or emergency.

958
01:18:25.676 --> 01:18:27.428
Your current location

959
01:18:28.509 --> 01:18:31.011
is Building A. 31st floor VIP lounge.

960
01:18:31.011 --> 01:18:32.012
Damn it...

961
01:18:35.146 --> 01:18:36.187
Hurry!

962
01:18:53.914 --> 01:18:55.956
What. you killed it?

963
01:18:56.667 --> 01:18:57.918
You said they're patients!

964
01:18:58.499 --> 01:19:00.381
You said we can't kill patients!

965
01:19:03.214 --> 01:19:05.466
What now? Where should we go?

966
01:19:07.508 --> 01:19:08.639
Turn around and run!

967
01:19:08.639 --> 01:19:11.051
Turn around? Come on. hurry!

968
01:19:16.517 --> 01:19:17.808
You asshole!

969
01:19:20.271 --> 01:19:21.101
Hurry!

970
01:19:21.652 --> 01:19:22.853
Save me!

971
01:19:45.966 --> 01:19:46.877
Save me...

972
01:19:48.088 --> 01:19:51.182
You said you're a cop... how could you?

973
01:19:52.843 --> 01:19:54.094
Shit!

974
01:20:38.349 --> 01:20:40.020
Take me. you bastard!

975
01:20:40.181 --> 01:20:40.811
Let go!

976
01:20:40.811 --> 01:20:42.733
Save me!

977
01:20:43.023 --> 01:20:44.485
Let go!

978
01:20:47.488 --> 01:20:49.069
Save me. you asshole!

979
01:20:51.111 --> 01:20:53.073
Let go of me. you bastard!

980
01:20:54.034 --> 01:20:55.156
Let go!

981
01:20:57.908 --> 01:20:58.909
Shit.

982
01:21:06.837 --> 01:21:08.088
For fuck's sake...

983
01:21:34.575 --> 01:21:35.696
What do we do now?

984
01:21:36.036 --> 01:21:37.908
How can we get to the rescue team?

985
01:21:48.799 --> 01:21:51.342
We have to be quiet. Let's communicate only by texting.

986
01:21:59.220 --> 01:22:00.721
Then what should we do now?

987
01:22:05.146 --> 01:22:06.687
Too dangerous to go to the rescue team.

988
01:22:06.687 --> 01:22:07.438
We need to make them come to us.

989
01:22:10.981 --> 01:22:14.024
How do we contact the rescue team?

990
01:22:19.580 --> 01:22:21.582
What are you talking about?

991
01:22:22.163 --> 01:22:23.624
I want to know too.

992
01:22:23.624 --> 01:22:24.785
Son of a bitch...

993
01:22:26.287 --> 01:22:27.418
I'll get the dead policeman's phone

994
01:22:27.418 --> 01:22:28.339
and contact the rescue team.

995
01:22:28.339 --> 01:22:29.960
You stay and watch over Suh.

996
01:23:01.492 --> 01:23:04.124
I'll get the dead policeman's phone

997
01:23:04.124 --> 01:23:06.327
and contact the rescue team.

998
01:23:10.631 --> 01:23:12.633
I think I found it!

999
01:23:13.133 --> 01:23:14.335
Put it up on the screen.

1000
01:23:18.889 --> 01:23:20.090
Who is that?

1001
01:23:22.303 --> 01:23:23.844
Kang Woo-cheol...

1002
01:23:24.145 --> 01:23:27.188
Chains Bio CEO Kang Woo-cheol was the first to be infected.

1003
01:23:27.518 --> 01:23:30.060
Track him and find out where he is now.

1004
01:23:30.271 --> 01:23:31.312
Yes. sir.

1005
01:23:38.859 --> 01:23:41.282
Is she just going to go off with the rescue team?

1006
01:23:42.112 --> 01:23:44.415
What if she just leaves us behind?

1007
01:23:45.166 --> 01:23:46.537
Don't you get it?

1008
01:23:46.667 --> 01:23:49.039
Without him. the rescue team's not coming anyway.

1009
01:23:49.420 --> 01:23:51.212
And don't talk for no reason.

1010
01:23:51.672 --> 01:23:53.624
He hears everything we say.

1011
01:23:53.874 --> 01:23:54.755
Fuck.

1012
01:23:55.546 --> 01:23:57.468
We're screwed anyway.

1013
01:23:58.799 --> 01:24:00.971
The cop died. all of them died...

1014
01:24:04.765 --> 01:24:07.978
How can you stay so calm in this situation?

1015
01:24:10.691 --> 01:24:11.892
Because it was even worse.

1016
01:24:13.814 --> 01:24:17.738
With you and your gang bullying me. every day was hell.

1017
01:24:18.319 --> 01:24:19.780
Worse than this.

1018
01:24:23.154 --> 01:24:24.325
I'm sorry.

1019
01:24:25.956 --> 01:24:26.907
What?

1020
01:24:28.159 --> 01:24:29.750
I said sorry.

1021
01:24:30.911 --> 01:24:33.003
For everything I did to you.

1022
01:24:35.085 --> 01:24:36.467
All of a sudden?

1023
01:24:38.299 --> 01:24:39.590
Now?

1024
01:24:40.671 --> 01:24:42.973
After all the bullying you did?

1025
01:24:43.594 --> 01:24:46.136
I said. I'm sorry!

1026
01:24:46.727 --> 01:24:49.310
But it's all over now!

1027
01:24:50.351 --> 01:24:53.023
We're going to die here.

1028
01:24:53.734 --> 01:24:55.276
That woman.

1029
01:24:56.487 --> 01:24:58.319
she'll come for us. for sure.

1030
01:24:59.240 --> 01:25:02.533
And we'll get out of here alive.

1031
01:25:03.494 --> 01:25:05.446
So stop crying.

1032
01:25:06.197 --> 01:25:07.328
I'm sorry.

1033
01:25:08.699 --> 01:25:10.621
I'm sorry. So-eun.

1034
01:25:12.623 --> 01:25:14.084
If you want to apologize to me.

1035
01:25:14.124 --> 01:25:15.916
do it properly once this is all over.

1036
01:25:20.881 --> 01:25:21.962
All right.

1037
01:25:52.163 --> 01:25:54.585
Police Commissioner Park Jeong-hwan

1038
01:26:05.306 --> 01:26:06.507
Officer Lee.

1039
01:26:06.557 --> 01:26:07.598
Where are you?

1040
01:26:07.638 --> 01:26:09.310
Do you have Suh with you?

1041
01:26:09.640 --> 01:26:11.101
You subordinate was killed.

1042
01:26:11.101 --> 01:26:12.723
What? Who are you?

1043
01:26:14.645 --> 01:26:16.016
Who are you?

1044
01:26:16.857 --> 01:26:18.229
My name's Kwon Se-jeong.

1045
01:26:18.569 --> 01:26:21.111
I'm one of the people who've been holding Suh Young-chul.

1046
01:26:21.822 --> 01:26:23.194
Where is Suh now?

1047
01:26:23.234 --> 01:26:26.327
He's confined in a safe place.

1048
01:26:26.527 --> 01:26:29.079
Send the rescue team to where we are.

1049
01:26:29.830 --> 01:26:32.122
I found the current location of the first infected!

1050
01:26:32.283 --> 01:26:33.534
Where is it?

1051
01:26:33.534 --> 01:26:35.536
Building C. 15th floor hallway.

1052
01:26:35.586 --> 01:26:37.208
Then what should we do?

1053
01:26:38.289 --> 01:26:40.751
Divide the rescue team on the roof into two teams.

1054
01:26:40.921 --> 01:26:42.593
One team will secure Suh.

1055
01:26:42.593 --> 01:26:45.636
and the other will go kill the first infected.

1056
01:26:45.676 --> 01:26:47.178
as the professor said.

1057
01:26:47.298 --> 01:26:51.101
Even if we can't treat them. we need to secure the vaccine.

1058
01:26:52.102 --> 01:26:54.435
Listen. where is Suh Young-chul now?

1059
01:26:54.515 --> 01:26:56.106
We'll send a rescue team immediately.

1060
01:26:56.187 --> 01:26:59.440
The warehouse in Building A. 32nd floor. Come quickly.

1061
01:27:54.325 --> 01:27:55.826
Approaching the target.

1062
01:27:55.866 --> 01:27:58.078
Destination is beyond this hallway.

1063
01:28:02.293 --> 01:28:04.335
Infected at 12 o'clock!

1064
01:28:14.805 --> 01:28:15.726
Shoot them

1065
01:28:20.641 --> 01:28:22.483
Alpha Team. report location.

1066
01:28:23.103 --> 01:28:25.146
Moving to target in Building A.

1067
01:28:38.459 --> 01:28:40.661
Are you in there? We're the rescue team.

1068
01:28:41.832 --> 01:28:43.914
They're here! - Open the door. We're the rescue team.

1069
01:28:43.964 --> 01:28:45.085
Yes!

1070
01:28:45.085 --> 01:28:46.377
Na-yoon!

1071
01:28:47.968 --> 01:28:49.170
We're the rescue team.

1072
01:29:37.308 --> 01:29:38.809
You said you'd apologize?

1073
01:29:39.890 --> 01:29:41.312
Do it now.

1074
01:29:44.855 --> 01:29:45.936
Fuck!

1075
01:29:47.107 --> 01:29:47.938
Go away!

1076
01:29:51.031 --> 01:29:52.443
Stay away. you monster!

1077
01:29:57.328 --> 01:29:58.579
No!

1078
01:30:05.586 --> 01:30:06.247
Clear!

1079
01:30:06.297 --> 01:30:07.878
Passage secured. Re-entering.

1080
01:30:12.963 --> 01:30:14.215
Target in sight!

1081
01:30:14.385 --> 01:30:15.676
There he is. there...

1082
01:30:35.406 --> 01:30:36.827
Huh. why'd it go off?

1083
01:30:36.987 --> 01:30:37.948
Why'd it go off?

1084
01:30:37.948 --> 01:30:38.989
Try connecting again.

1085
01:30:51.592 --> 01:30:53.294
Confirmed dead.

1086
01:30:54.885 --> 01:30:57.047
It's over now. right?

1087
01:30:58.349 --> 01:31:00.261
They've all stopped?

1088
01:31:02.603 --> 01:31:03.894
What's that?

1089
01:31:15.236 --> 01:31:16.567
Requesting backup!

1090
01:31:21.202 --> 01:31:22.283
Requesting backup!

1091
01:31:27.378 --> 01:31:28.789
And Suh Young-chul?

1092
01:31:29.380 --> 01:31:30.921
Isn't that him?

1093
01:31:31.922 --> 01:31:33.043
There!

1094
01:32:28.389 --> 01:32:30.391
Those idiots.

1095
01:34:27.218 --> 01:34:28.389
No!

1096
01:34:33.684 --> 01:34:34.895
Get a grip.

1097
01:34:35.476 --> 01:34:38.649
If you kill Suh now. more people will be in danger.

1098
01:34:38.939 --> 01:34:41.071
What do I care about that now?

1099
01:34:41.522 --> 01:34:42.363
Hey!

1100
01:34:44.325 --> 01:34:45.486
You people...

1101
01:34:46.197 --> 01:34:48.369
You abandoned my sister!

1102
01:35:09.550 --> 01:35:11.642
Want me to make your wish come true?

1103
01:35:13.144 --> 01:35:14.515
What did you say?

1104
01:35:22.153 --> 01:35:23.154
Hyun-hee?

1105
01:36:21.332 --> 01:36:22.543
Did you see that?

1106
01:36:23.464 --> 01:36:25.176
Doesn't she look much better?

1107
01:36:25.796 --> 01:36:27.298
Professor Kwon?

1108
01:36:29.800 --> 01:36:31.632
You sent this invitation. didn't you?

1109
01:36:32.973 --> 01:36:35.726
My inspiration to create these children

1110
01:36:35.726 --> 01:36:37.938
came from you. Professor Kwon.

1111
01:36:41.392 --> 01:36:44.395
My dad begged you.

1112
01:36:49.150 --> 01:36:50.611
To Prof. Kwon: Imperfect communication.

1113
01:36:50.651 --> 01:36:51.612
the source of all tragedy

1114
01:36:51.612 --> 01:36:53.454
Se-jeong. this is a misunderstanding.

1115
01:36:53.534 --> 01:36:56.157
The law doesn't always match the actual situation.

1116
01:36:56.787 --> 01:36:59.290
Borrowing the name of students who didn't take part

1117
01:36:59.460 --> 01:37:02.713
was the only way to pay students who did participate.

1118
01:37:02.963 --> 01:37:04.715
They all agreed to it.

1119
01:37:04.965 --> 01:37:07.338
No. no. Se-jeong...

1120
01:37:07.338 --> 01:37:11.262
This is a tragedy resulting from imperfect communication.

1121
01:37:12.343 --> 01:37:13.384
No. please.

1122
01:37:13.724 --> 01:37:15.135
Se-jeong... Se-jeong?

1123
01:37:29.990 --> 01:37:33.194
And so. all of this was because of that incident?

1124
01:37:34.495 --> 01:37:36.747
If you want revenge. take it out on me. asshole!

1125
01:37:37.698 --> 01:37:38.909
What revenge?

1126
01:37:40.251 --> 01:37:42.203
My dad's death

1127
01:37:44.205 --> 01:37:47.127
was a tragedy caused by imperfect communication.

1128
01:37:47.708 --> 01:37:49.840
Not because of someone like you.

1129
01:37:49.840 --> 01:37:53.304
Like you... like you...

1130
01:37:55.386 --> 01:37:58.018
Compared to the great achievements of mankind.

1131
01:37:58.179 --> 01:37:59.350
the knowledge possessed

1132
01:37:59.350 --> 01:38:01.432
by any individual is incredibly limited.

1133
01:38:02.022 --> 01:38:06.687
That limitation creates a state of terrible incomprehension.

1134
01:38:07.728 --> 01:38:10.571
In the end. the way to stop all such tragedies

1135
01:38:10.941 --> 01:38:15.286
is to connect all of our minds together.

1136
01:38:16.867 --> 01:38:19.370
The imperfect communication of human beings.

1137
01:38:19.740 --> 01:38:21.582
all the tragedies that result from

1138
01:38:21.622 --> 01:38:23.874
not fully understanding what others feel.

1139
01:38:24.625 --> 01:38:26.877
This system is the perfect solution.

1140
01:38:27.958 --> 01:38:29.960
That's what we are.

1141
01:38:32.173 --> 01:38:36.347
What do less evolved beings like you have over us?

1142
01:38:37.348 --> 01:38:38.469
Ah ...

1143
01:38:39.310 --> 01:38:41.352
The freedom to be an outcast?

1144
01:38:42.933 --> 01:38:45.065
Can you handle that. Professor?

1145
01:38:46.647 --> 01:38:48.729
You do this because you can handle it?

1146
01:38:49.900 --> 01:38:52.112
Then go ahead. be an outcast.

1147
01:39:02.783 --> 01:39:04.415
Alpha Team. target located.

1148
01:39:16.257 --> 01:39:18.509
Alpha Team. vaccine secured! Vaccine secured!

1149
01:39:18.799 --> 01:39:20.761
If target's secured. withdraw quickly!

1150
01:39:52.213 --> 01:39:55.636
Well. it's a shame. but at least we've got the vaccine...

1151
01:39:58.008 --> 01:39:59.550
Then what about her?

1152
01:40:00.090 --> 01:40:02.052
You're just going to abandon her?

1153
01:40:02.473 --> 01:40:04.805
Send the rescue team back in now!

1154
01:40:05.266 --> 01:40:06.727
Okay. everyone...

1155
01:40:06.847 --> 01:40:08.899
Professor. get some rest. okay?

1156
01:40:09.150 --> 01:40:10.941
I think your job here is done.

1157
01:40:11.152 --> 01:40:13.604
Escort the professor out. Back to your places.

1158
01:40:13.694 --> 01:40:15.526
- This way. please. - Let go!

1159
01:40:18.108 --> 01:40:20.321
Alpha Team moving to Building C Rooftop.

1160
01:40:20.321 --> 01:40:23.033
Roger. Charlie Team ready to move to adjacent building.

1161
01:40:39.009 --> 01:40:42.183
My Better Half

1162
01:40:46.307 --> 01:40:47.598
Hello?

1163
01:40:47.808 --> 01:40:51.272
Hello? Professor Kwon? Are you okay?

1164
01:40:52.483 --> 01:40:55.105
I know your situation there.

1165
01:40:55.446 --> 01:40:57.027
You know my situation?

1166
01:40:57.898 --> 01:41:01.822
I was watching from the Counterterrorism HQ.

1167
01:41:02.743 --> 01:41:03.824
I'm sorry.

1168
01:41:04.365 --> 01:41:07.328
I don't think the rescue team can go back.

1169
01:41:10.211 --> 01:41:12.913
Then why are you calling me?

1170
01:41:15.376 --> 01:41:18.128
I thought I had found a way to stop the infected.

1171
01:41:18.719 --> 01:41:22.052
There was a group of monkeys Suh experimented on at his lab.

1172
01:41:22.223 --> 01:41:24.845
When a monkey marked #1 was killed.

1173
01:41:25.015 --> 01:41:27.558
all the other monkeys stopped moving.

1174
01:41:27.678 --> 01:41:28.679
They stopped moving?

1175
01:41:29.270 --> 01:41:31.682
So I thought killing the first infected

1176
01:41:31.682 --> 01:41:33.314
would solve everything...

1177
01:41:41.282 --> 01:41:42.993
The monkey marked #1

1178
01:41:43.194 --> 01:41:45.326
It's not the first one to be infected.

1179
01:41:45.576 --> 01:41:47.788
It's the monkey that controls all the others.

1180
01:41:47.948 --> 01:41:50.201
In that case. monkey #1 is

1181
01:41:51.202 --> 01:41:52.953
Suh Young-chul himself.

1182
01:41:53.544 --> 01:41:55.876
Alpha Team arriving at destination.

1183
01:41:56.086 --> 01:41:57.708
Have you ever been shot?

1184
01:41:58.549 --> 01:41:59.710
Eyes forward.

1185
01:42:21.482 --> 01:42:23.154
I'm so sore.

1186
01:42:44.755 --> 01:42:46.557
Tell them to kill Suh Young-chul immediately.

1187
01:42:46.557 --> 01:42:49.180
That'll stop all of them from moving.

1188
01:42:49.600 --> 01:42:51.972
If Suh gets outside. we're finished!

1189
01:42:52.973 --> 01:42:55.896
We can't. If we kill him now.

1190
01:42:56.267 --> 01:42:58.359
not only the victims' families.

1191
01:42:58.729 --> 01:43:00.901
but everyone scared of getting infected

1192
01:43:00.901 --> 01:43:02.273
will become our enemies.

1193
01:43:02.323 --> 01:43:04.775
The government won't easily make that decision.

1194
01:43:05.866 --> 01:43:07.698
Can you handle that?

1195
01:43:08.199 --> 01:43:10.581
Then go ahead. be an outcast.

1196
01:43:12.623 --> 01:43:14.285
So that's what he meant.

1197
01:43:30.181 --> 01:43:32.012
Is he really the vaccine?

1198
01:43:32.973 --> 01:43:36.267
Never mind what others think. what do you think?

1199
01:43:39.059 --> 01:43:40.941
You have to decide.

1200
01:43:56.707 --> 01:43:59.460
Any issues bringing Suh Young-chul outside?

1201
01:43:59.880 --> 01:44:02.923
No. Suh Young-chul is coming out safely.

1202
01:44:11.972 --> 01:44:13.684
We need to eliminate Suh Young-chul!

1203
01:44:14.555 --> 01:44:15.976
What are you talking about?

1204
01:44:16.227 --> 01:44:18.479
I called Professor Kwon who's in the building now.

1205
01:44:18.649 --> 01:44:21.812
and she said Suh is controlling all of the infected.

1206
01:44:21.812 --> 01:44:22.903
Suh Young-chul is #1.

1207
01:44:22.983 --> 01:44:24.525
We need to kill him.

1208
01:44:24.985 --> 01:44:27.608
Seriously? Kill the vaccine?

1209
01:44:29.360 --> 01:44:30.991
Your responsibility extends only

1210
01:44:31.031 --> 01:44:33.033
to that operation that failed earlier!

1211
01:44:33.324 --> 01:44:35.286
Does anyone have clear evidence

1212
01:44:35.286 --> 01:44:37.578
that we need to kill our only vaccine?

1213
01:44:37.618 --> 01:44:39.079
Anyone? Anyone have it?

1214
01:44:41.502 --> 01:44:45.426
The vaccine is on his way here now. It's all finished!

1215
01:44:47.968 --> 01:44:50.881
HQ. lifting lockdown here. One SWAT vehicle moving.

1216
01:44:50.881 --> 01:44:52.723
The vaccine is being moved to the safe zone.

1217
01:44:54.014 --> 01:44:56.887
HQ. vehicle has entered! I repeat. vehicle has entered!

1218
01:45:03.894 --> 01:45:05.526
Too many people are gathered in front

1219
01:45:05.566 --> 01:45:07.358
of Doongwoori Building. Support needed.

1220
01:45:07.698 --> 01:45:09.400
Requesting all available personnel

1221
01:45:09.400 --> 01:45:11.202
to be sent to Doongwoori Building.

1222
01:47:06.147 --> 01:47:08.519
Secure the area! Move back!

1223
01:47:09.069 --> 01:47:10.691
Stop. please. Move back.

1224
01:47:10.821 --> 01:47:12.443
Move back. move back!

1225
01:47:46.977 --> 01:47:48.519
Minister!

1226
01:47:54.114 --> 01:47:55.366
The barricade in front of

1227
01:47:55.366 --> 01:47:57.318
Doongwoori Building is being breached!

1228
01:47:57.568 --> 01:47:58.779
What?

1229
01:48:25.726 --> 01:48:26.977
Come on.

1230
01:48:33.654 --> 01:48:36.357
No... we need to get Suh.

1231
01:48:36.487 --> 01:48:38.279
Where are the nearest army units?

1232
01:48:39.029 --> 01:48:42.823
All the troops in Seoul are mobilized in there.

1233
01:48:44.325 --> 01:48:45.416
Damn it!

1234
01:48:45.666 --> 01:48:48.919
Listen. everyone. Let's disband for now. okay?

1235
01:48:48.959 --> 01:48:51.462
We'll decide the HQ's new location later.

1236
01:48:51.502 --> 01:48:53.334
Everyone evacuate. quickly!

1237
01:49:33.414 --> 01:49:34.505
Hello?

1238
01:49:34.835 --> 01:49:36.667
What happened to Suh?

1239
01:49:37.378 --> 01:49:39.760
The people in charge here are all running away.

1240
01:49:40.010 --> 01:49:41.762
And Suh Young-chul escaped.

1241
01:49:43.344 --> 01:49:46.387
Can you check Suh's location? You said you saw everything.

1242
01:49:46.477 --> 01:49:48.889
Just a minute. I'll call you right back.

1243
01:49:50.231 --> 01:49:51.392
Professor Gong.

1244
01:49:52.102 --> 01:49:53.314
Professor Gong!

1245
01:50:04.114 --> 01:50:05.576
Do we know Suh's location?

1246
01:50:05.616 --> 01:50:06.537
What?

1247
01:50:06.867 --> 01:50:08.289
What are you doing?

1248
01:50:08.579 --> 01:50:09.660
You need to evacuate!

1249
01:50:09.910 --> 01:50:11.662
There's no time! Go. quickly!

1250
01:50:24.265 --> 01:50:25.466
I found him.

1251
01:50:26.347 --> 01:50:28.309
He's at 32 Sinsok Street. on the main road.

1252
01:50:31.972 --> 01:50:33.814
See the car with blinking lights?

1253
01:50:34.275 --> 01:50:35.226
I see it.

1254
01:50:35.276 --> 01:50:36.437
I'm watching.

1255
01:50:39.400 --> 01:50:41.071
Tell me which way to go.

1256
01:50:48.239 --> 01:50:49.410
Keep going straight.

1257
01:50:49.410 --> 01:50:49.950
Keep going straight.

1258
01:50:51.912 --> 01:50:53.494
Left at the intersection.

1259
01:50:59.460 --> 01:51:00.841
Turn right at the next intersection.

1260
01:53:09.630 --> 01:53:11.512
That idiot. covering himself in that...

1261
01:53:18.889 --> 01:53:19.980
Move!

1262
01:53:22.523 --> 01:53:24.605
Out of the way!

1263
01:53:50.591 --> 01:53:51.842
reverted to their original state.

1264
01:54:38.519 --> 01:54:40.601
Stop! Stop. you bastards!

1265
01:54:41.222 --> 01:54:42.563
Stop!

1266
01:54:55.406 --> 01:54:57.448
Please stop!

1267
01:55:03.704 --> 01:55:04.545
Stop!

1268
01:55:04.915 --> 01:55:06.086
Please...

1269
01:56:54.775 --> 01:56:55.446
Yes?

1270
01:56:55.446 --> 01:56:57.698
How's it in other places? Was it successful?

1271
01:57:00.781 --> 01:57:02.363
They've stopped.

1272
01:57:03.824 --> 01:57:05.496
You did it.

1273
01:57:06.497 --> 01:57:09.250
I doubt people will see it that way.

1274
01:57:10.120 --> 01:57:11.582
What should we do?

1275
01:57:11.752 --> 01:57:13.924
The vaccine's gone for good now.

1276
01:57:13.924 --> 01:57:15.966
Everyone's going to hate me.

1277
01:57:17.338 --> 01:57:18.719
Don't worry.

1278
01:57:18.839 --> 01:57:21.342
I'll testify with you.

1279
01:57:21.842 --> 01:57:25.135
If you're going to be hated. I'll take it with you.

1280
01:57:30.941 --> 01:57:32.773
No need for that.

1281
01:57:32.943 --> 01:57:34.695
I'm used to people hating me.

1282
01:57:36.737 --> 01:57:38.449
Where are you now?

1283
01:57:39.740 --> 01:57:42.323
I guess we have a lot of work ahead of us.

1284
01:57:43.305 --> 01:58:43.211
